  "title": "Sales Support (Assistant)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Support the sales team with order processing, quotations, pricing updates, and customer coordination</li><li>Prepare sales reports, forecasts, and market analysis for management review</li><li>Liaise with customers on order status, delivery schedules, and documentation</li><li>Assist in improving sales processes and documentation workflows</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>At least Diploma in any discipline</li><li>At least 1 years of working experience</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving skills</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Positive attitude, willingness to learn, and adaptability</li><li>Strong sense of responsibility and team-oriented mindset<br /></li></ul>",
